[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.26,
    "text": "Now, here's the deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.26,
    "endTime": 7.3999999999999995,
    "text": "I will make you a potion that will turn you into a human for three days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.4,
    "endTime": 8.233,
    "text": "Got that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.233,
    "endTime": 10.258000000000001,
    "text": "Three days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.258,
    "endTime": 12.7,
    "text": "♪ I can read your future ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.7,
    "endTime": 15.357,
    "text": "♪ I can change it around some, too ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.357,
    "endTime": 18.599999999999998,
    "text": "♪ I look deep into your heart and soul ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.6,
    "endTime": 20.400000000000002,
    "text": "You do have a soul, don't you, Lawrence?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.4,
    "endTime": 23.7,
    "text": "♪ Make your wildest dreams come true ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.7,
    "endTime": 26.4,
    "text": "Take her far into the forest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.4,
    "endTime": 32.699999999999996,
    "text": "Find some secluded glade where she can pick wildflowers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.7,
    "endTime": 34.7,
    "text": "Yes, Your Majesty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.7,
    "endTime": 40.800000000000004,
    "text": "And there, my faithful huntsman, you will kill her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.8,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "But Your Majesty, the little Princess!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 45.576,
    "text": "Silence!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 50.442,
    "text": "You know the penalty if you fail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.442,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "Yes, Your Majesty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 65.271,
    "text": "But to make doubly sure you do not fail, bring back her heart in this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.3,
    "endTime": 70.1,
    "text": "And you're not offended, Your Excellency?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.1,
    "endTime": 73.69999999999999,
    "text": "Why no, Your Majesty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.7,
    "endTime": 81.7,
    "text": "And to show I bear no ill will, I, too, shall bestow a gift on the child."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.7,
    "endTime": 85.601,
    "text": "Listen well, all of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.08,
    "endTime": 91.8,
    "text": "The Princess shall indeed grow in grace and beauty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.8,
    "endTime": 96.212,
    "text": "Beloved by all who know her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.212,
    "endTime": 108.8,
    "text": "But, before the sun sets on her 16th birthday, she shall prick her finger on the spindle of a spinning wheel and die!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.8,
    "endTime": 111.634,
    "text": "Oh no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 113.7,
    "text": "Seize that creature!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.7,
    "endTime": 116.552,
    "text": "Stand back, you fools."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.146,
    "endTime": 126.7,
    "text": "Stop fighting me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.7,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "No, I won't stop!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 132.31,
    "text": "For every minute of the rest of my life I will fight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.31,
    "endTime": 136.016,
    "text": "I will never stop trying to get away from you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.3,
    "endTime": 144.746,
    "text": "But, if you let me save him, I will go with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.746,
    "endTime": 145.3,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.3,
    "endTime": 147.143,
    "text": "No Rapunzel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.143,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "I'll never run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 150.7,
    "text": "I'll never try to escape."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.7,
    "endTime": 155.14,
    "text": "Just let me heal him and you and I will be together forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.14,
    "endTime": 156.7,
    "text": "Just like you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.7,
    "endTime": 160.01,
    "text": "Everything will be the way it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.01,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "I promise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "Just like you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 175.7,
    "text": "Just let me heal him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.7,
    "endTime": 179.91299999999998,
    "text": "In case you get any ideas about following us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.292,
    "endTime": 184.7,
    "text": "♪ It's the green, it's the green, it's the green you need ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.7,
    "endTime": 186.219,
    "text": "♪ And when I looked into your future ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.219,
    "endTime": 188.79999999999998,
    "text": "♪ It's the green that I see ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.8,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "♪ On you little man ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "♪ I don't wanna waste much time ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 195.5,
    "text": "♪ You've been pushed around all your life ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.5,
    "endTime": 197.8,
    "text": "♪ You've been pushed around by your mother ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.8,
    "endTime": 200.4,
    "text": "♪ And your sister and your brother ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.4,
    "endTime": 203.017,
    "text": "♪ And if you was married ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.017,
    "endTime": 206.4,
    "text": "♪ You'd be pushed around by your wife ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.4,
    "endTime": 210.70000000000002,
    "text": "♪ But in your future, the you I see ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.7,
    "endTime": 215.39999999999998,
    "text": "♪ Is exactly the man you always wanted to be ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.5,
    "endTime": 217.7,
    "text": "Shake my hand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.7,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "Come on, boys, won't you shake a poor sinner's hand?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 228.7,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.7,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "♪ Are you ready ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "♪ Are you ready ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 234.7,
    "text": "♪ Are you ready ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.7,
    "endTime": 236.0,
    "text": "♪ Transformation central ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.2,
    "endTime": 237.7,
    "text": "♪ Transformation central ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.7,
    "endTime": 239.0,
    "text": "♪ Reformation central ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.0,
    "endTime": 240.5,
    "text": "♪ Reformation central ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.5,
    "endTime": 243.6,
    "text": "♪ Transmodification central ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.6,
    "endTime": 245.7,
    "text": "♪ Can you feel it ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.7,
    "endTime": 247.393,
    "text": "♪ You're changing, you're changing ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.393,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "♪ You're changing all right ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 253.8,
    "text": "♪ I hope you're satisfied ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.8,
    "endTime": 257.302,
    "text": "♪ But if you ain't, don't blame me ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.302,
    "endTime": 259.391,
    "text": "♪ You can blame my friends ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.391,
    "endTime": 264.0,
    "text": "♪ On the other side ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 265.265,
    "text": "♪ You got what you wanted ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.353,
    "endTime": 273.271,
    "text": "♪ But you lost what you had ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.271,
    "endTime": 281.887,
    "text": "♪ This poor unfortunate soul ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.279,
    "endTime": 290.86,
    "text": "♪ Come winds of the Caspian Sea ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.079,
    "endTime": 304.7,
    "text": "Now sing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.7,
    "endTime": 307.529,
    "text": "Keep singing!"
  }
]